                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman.</hi>) On the 9th of Sept. I heard the prose<lb></lb>cutor give an alarm—I stopped the prisoner with this pair of trowsers—he said, "Oh, it is not me, let me go"—I took him to the shop.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> My mother sent me into the shop about the trowsers, and I ran out to fetch the money with the trowsers in my hand.</p>
